milestones.description: Wasim Raja has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for PAK, going past Sarfraz Nawaz's 2
Wasim Bari has broken the record for most ODIs (4) as captain for PAK, going past Intikhab Alam
Wasim Bari has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (12) for PAK, going past Wasim Raja
Constant has broken the record for officiating the most ODIs (10) as an umpire, going past Dickie Bird
Liaqat Ali and Sikander Bakht's 24-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 20 between Asif Masood and Sarfraz Nawaz
